OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FITV News Scotland Reporter Louise
OL,7,FScott meets concerned workers in
OL,8,FAberdeen as the oil and gas industry
OL,9,Ftakes a hit due to net zero policy
OL,11,FThe oil and gas industry was once a
OL,12,Fjob for life but now it's shrouded in
OL,13,Funcertainty.
OL,15,FExperts have warned the transition to
OL,16,Frenewable energy could lead to
OL,17,Fthousands of job losses.
