OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FThe Scottish city of Aberdeen has long
OL,7,Fbeen known as the oil capital of
OL,8,FEurope after reserves were first
OL,9,Fdiscovered off the North Sea just over
OL,10,Ffive decades ago.
OL,12,FBut now, the once bustling main
OL,13,Fshopping area, Union Street, is
OL,14,Flittered with empty units.
OL,16,FThe downturn in oil has led to a
OL,17,Fstagnant property market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
