OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FRussell Borthwick, Aberdeen Chamber of
OL,7,FCommerce, said: "We've had a number of
OL,8,Fyears now where the key sector that
OL,9,Fdrives the economy of this region has
OL,10,Fbeen under pressure - that never more
OL,11,Fso than now.
OL,13,F"Workers from the city, who are just
OL,14,Fback from three weeks on the oil rigs,
OL,15,Ftell me 'everybody worries for the
OL,16,Ffuture'."
OL,18,FExperts say the growth in renewable
OL,19,Fenergy is not matching the rate the
OL,20,Fgas and oil industry is declining.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
