OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FProfessor Paul de Leeuw, director of
OL,7,Fthe RGU Energy Transition Institute,
OL,8,Fat Robert Gordon University, said: "At
OL,9,Fthe moment we see the oil and gas
OL,10,Findustry declining quite fast.
OL,12,F"But the renewables industry is not
OL,13,Fhappening fast enough, so we have a
OL,14,Freal issue."
OL,16,F"What we do with the supply chain,
OL,17,Fwhat do with the workforce?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
