OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FAlready, #420 million has been spent
OL,7,Fon Aberdeen's new port - the majority
OL,8,Fof business is still with oil and gas
OL,9,F- so the move to green energy has to
OL,10,Fbe carefully balanced.
OL,12,FPort of Aberdeen Chief Commercial
OL,13,FOfficer, Roddy James said: "We all
OL,14,Fknow that the oil and gas industry is
OL,15,Fdecreasing and declining, but it also
OL,16,Fcan't go off a cliff edge because if
OL,17,Fit does, then you've got this big gap
OL,18,Ffor the new investment comes into
OL,19,Frenewables, which we believe is
OL,20,Fbetween four and five years away."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
