OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FIn the UK one in 220 jobs is in the
OL,7,Foffshore energy industry, in Scotland,
OL,8,Fthat increases to one in 13, and in
OL,9,Fthe country's northeast it is one in
OL,10,Ffive.
OL,12,FThis means any major change to the
OL,13,Fgovernment's energy policy would have
OL,14,Fthe most significant impact on this
OL,15,Fpart of the country.
OL,17,FWith the election campaign well
OL,18,Funderway, the focus has turned to
OL,19,Fwhich party will support the sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
