OL,3,CUncertainty for Aberdeen's oil and gas
OL,4,Cindustry over the race to net zero
OL,6,FThe race for net zero carbon emissions
OL,7,Fis a major policy challenge for
OL,8,Fwhoever forms the next government.
OL,10,FConservatives say they would grant new
OL,11,Foil and gas fields, Labour say they
OL,12,Fwon't, and the SNP have changed their
OL,13,Fstance and now say they would grant if
OL,14,Fit met their climate criteria.
OL,16,FThe Lib Dems and Greens meanwhile say
OL,17,Fthe focus should be on bolstering the
OL,18,Frenewable industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
